Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:27.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It's really Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NBut why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:13.93,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,And she's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I was afraid I'd lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But why... did she\Nchange Selectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThat's only half of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering why Urith\Nis even battling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,She's supposed to be\Ncarrying out your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,right now, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, she's not\Nbreaking any rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, to a certain extent, my\Nwish has already been granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,But what does she have\Nto gain from fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSpill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something\Nyou're not telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:50.00,Main,,0,0,0,,About Urith and about Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.09,0:02:51.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.34,Main,,0,0,0,,That's just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Tasteless and cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NPoor little Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.56,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a frightening\Nworld out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You're only going\Nto be hurt again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Lucky us, we get to go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Now Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hoo-yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Try not to\Nhumiliate us too badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have to ask you\Nto stop distracting my LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,The only one she\Nneeds to talk to is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish Crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.34,Main,,0,0,0,,So strong! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:39.76,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna blow me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, unless\NI blow you up first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We're like rivals, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA growls] Glad\Nsomebody's enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NChorizo the Fantasy! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,That is not the name of my move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:53.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then attack with\NCloth Crash Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:59.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[whoops] She's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so done...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,It's getting hard to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I think Chiyori's\Nas good as done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,This is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Tama! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh. It's all right--\Nyou don't have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.71,Main,,0,0,0,,to listen to her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.09,Main,,0,0,0,,She threw you away, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]\NShe did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,We just--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.47,0:04:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Use Spell: Get Bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA grunts] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, that's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.68,Main,,0,0,0,,--[TAMA growls]\N--[ELDORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems Tama's getting along\Nfine without her old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:35.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:38.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NYaaugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,If she can have fun in\Nbattle, why can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:50.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] She has a new partner,\Nbut nothing else has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI fought for this, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I fought for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:05:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,We were meant to be\Ntogether, to win together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[bells ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:10.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,And Tama's...\Nnot having fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:14.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NAh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Eldora, Grow!\NAttack with Kozame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NTama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI was a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why I got taken\Naway from you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.51,Main,,0,0,0,,ARTS: Baroque Defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NRrgh! Sh-Shira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NAw, c'mon, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She's using a card\Nthat blocks offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you pay attention?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:00.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NThis is awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.90,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought Battles were\Nsupposed to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I liked getting strong\Nand winning, but I hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,If I don't have Ru,\Nthen there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NSalvage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI think you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,She's really not having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NThis is all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I was sure beating\NIona would be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd given up any hope\Nof coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:41.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna turn\Ninto an LRIG for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.24,Main,,0,0,0,,But that didn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.03,Main,,0,0,0,,If I could change Yuzuki back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:46.66,Main,,0,0,0,,if I could give you\Na better life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,it was a small price to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.58,Main,,0,0,0,,At least, that's what\NI tried to convince myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:55.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I missed you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:07:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything feels empty\Nwithout you to share it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI did bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I was too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NSo was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,If I had just told you\Nhow I felt,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.09,Main,,0,0,0,,then this wouldn't\Nhave happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I was the one who\Nneeded to trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I was acting like\Nsome kind of lonely hero
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,and I got stuck\Nthinking that I needed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,to push everyone else away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But I should've let you help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:26.40,Main,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're my best friend\Nin the whole world, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NIt's not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:32.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NHer best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,--[ELDORA sighs]\N--[CHIYORI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Jeez. I understand why\Nthey're crying, but you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NI love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Their friendship\Nis so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,And now they gotta\Nfight each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,which is one of\Nthe best plot twists ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so cliché! It's like\Na TV show come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a good cliché!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, they're like\Nthe bread and butter of my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm so glad you're\Nenjoying this little drama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,while I'm getting\Ndestroyed out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NWha...? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Pretty sure they're\Ngonna finish me off
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,with the next move. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You naughty thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Thinking of another girl\Nwhile you're doing it with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You should be ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:34.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH whimper]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:03.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NIf you want her that bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.67,Main,,0,0,0,,why don't you battle me for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:16.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, you don't have to battle!\NShe can't make you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NHmph. No rush though,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:22.39,Main,,0,0,0,,you come find me when\Nyou're good and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Work on her for me, Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:28.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Till next time,\NMiss Pain-in-the-Ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]\NRu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NDon't worry. We can fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NYeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.22,Main,,0,0,0,,At least I know Tama's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:57.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Not only that, it seems like\Nshe feels the same way I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, thanks for\Nsticking with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,through all this mess, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NNice job on that plot twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,A tragedy among friends\Nand a rival for me! Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta admit,\Nthat was pretty sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys should be way\Nmore pumped about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:20.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, Eldora,\Nwhat the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Why would you\Ndo that after we told you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,how dangerous Battles were?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you even care what\Nhappens to Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Both of us spent a long time\Nworking all this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.13,Main,,0,0,0,,She can be pretty\Nstubborn, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:35.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NLet's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wa-pa-pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NChorizo De Ibéricoña The Second!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I've\Neaten chorizo before,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,but what does sausage\Nhave to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing--it's the name I'm gonna\Nhave when I turn into an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE, RUKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.95,Main,,0,0,0,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,There is no talking\Nsense into this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.53,Main,,0,0,0,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You lost your first match to me,\Nand now your second to Urith?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You're already down\Nto your last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYou gotta stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.83,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, I lost a couple,\Nbut I won three already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,That means my wish could\Ncome true at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but if you\Nlose one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.80,Main,,0,0,0,,that wish is gonna be corrupted!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.93,Main,,0,0,0,,The main character in\Nthe novel lost twice too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.05,Main,,0,0,0,,but she didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She beat her rival\Nand got her wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,She passes out, then finds\Nherself in the White Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,when she wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.19,Main,,0,0,0,,White Garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Duh, it's the\Nhyper-dimensional white void?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,White void? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds suspiciously\Nlike the white room I went to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,when I became an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean they talk\Nabout that in the book?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I so gave you a copy\Nof it, you should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're telling me\Nyou didn't read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I've... been\Nkind of busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,This is really getting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we see that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,The answers we need might be\Nright in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\N"WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,The Wings of Lament Mark the\NDreams of the Ruined Land."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.78,Main,,0,0,0,,By Fumio Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\N"In a future not far from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.78,Main,,0,0,0,,mysterious creatures\Nknown as LRIGs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.33,Main,,0,0,0,,appear all throughout\Nthe world."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] "Strange and beautiful,\Nthese fairy-like entities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.71,Main,,0,0,0,,form pacts with young girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.71,Main,,0,0,0,,promising that they can\Nmake their wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.79,0:12:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,However, for that to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,the girls must first\Nbattle other LRIGs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.22,Main,,0,0,0,,and collect something known\Nas WIXOSS factors
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,within their body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,A certain young girl forms a\Npartnership with a certain LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,and is drawn into\Nthe battle to make
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,her wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:48.77,Main,,0,0,0,,When she tastes\Nvictory at last,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.10,Main,,0,0,0,,her wish is not granted, but\Ninstead,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,she suddenly finds herself\Nlost in the labyrinth of time:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:56.19,Main,,0,0,0,,White Garden."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] It's just like\NYuzuki was saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,That must be the white room\Nwith the window, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] They don't use the word\N"Selector,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,but everything else here\Nmatches up almost perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:08.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, they barely\Neven spiced it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! And look, now the\NDark Lady of Atonement
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:13.21,Main,,0,0,0,,shows up--her name is Cocoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:14.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.34,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the ruler\Nof White Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.34,Main,,0,0,0,,An almighty being that\Nholds dominion over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.13,Main,,0,0,0,,all WIXOSS Battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Is she like\Nthe last boss or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it ends\Non such a cliffhanger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:29.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[groans] Dang it! The suspense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It's killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\N"Cocoon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The word "mayu" means\N"cocoon" doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NThat's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoever wrote this must know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.28,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:44.49,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got ourselves a lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,The next step is to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NFumio Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,She got her start by posting\Nstories on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:57.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess it was like\Nfan fiction at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,but some editor liked the story,\Nand it became official canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Any information on when\Nthe third book is coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,They say it's on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You think she's\Na Selector like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But then it seems strange\Nthat she would glamorize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:17.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Especially if she's heard about\NMayu and that White Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That means she also knows\Nhow dangerous it is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,to keep having Battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:23.90,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to find\Nsome way to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I want every bit of\Ninformation she's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NOkay, but like, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She might know more about Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Or more about Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,There was something\Nyou said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.17,Main,,0,0,0,,about Tama maybe being one\Nof the "special" ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:37.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NMm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] That is to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:44.13,Main,,0,0,0,,some Eternal Girls are more\N"special" than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] You may lack the power\Nto create this fairy tale ending
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:51.18,Main,,0,0,0,,you so desire, but there is\Nmagic yet in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NSomewhere deep down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like I might know how.\NLike I can help all the LRIGs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe turn them back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:01.23,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something\Nwe still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Something that might\Nhelp save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:05.57,Main,,0,0,0,,And everyone else, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a second,\Nwhere did Chiyori go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:08.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NYargh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE, RUKO gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU]\NToo bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,That's six wins\Nin a row for Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:14.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:16.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You are too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't\Neven win one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll have to eat this entire\Nbox of snacks myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps] Could you be\Nthe Sorceress of Blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,The Queen of the Innocent\Nand Danger Zone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.09,Main,,0,0,0,,of all WIXOSS players\Nin the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU chuckles]\NMy goodness, perhaps I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.89,Main,,0,0,0,,How 'bout a new bet:\Nif you beat me, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join\Nus for a few rounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:42.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NOoh! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.65,Main,,0,0,0,,We found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the author's website!\NAnd she updated recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NTo: Fumio Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:54.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Subject: Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:59.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse us for the sudden\NE-mail. We read your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.67,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be very up front.\NWe're Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you aware of Selectors?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If so, then, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:10.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Please allow us... the\Nopportunity to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko Kominato.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe Uemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that all sound good to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NCatch you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.11,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll give you a call\Nwhen we hear back from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You gotta come with us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NYou bet I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH laugh]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You think... she'll respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... I hope so, since\Nwe've got so many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.63,Main,,0,0,0,,We still don't know what\Nreally happened with Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Or with Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NMm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Either way, I don't think\Nit's a coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,that she ended up\Nwith Tama as her LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like me and Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,It is kinda fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu's plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:06.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Then we have to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:07.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm just trying to figure\Nout why she's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Does she like watching us\Nsuffer, or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] You're looking\Nat this all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:21.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop trying to apply\Nrules or logic to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Those are just a veil to\Nentangle players even further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:28.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu's plan isn't very complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:30.51,Main,,0,0,0,,All the players are her toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:33.05,Main,,0,0,0,,And now she's having\Nher way with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,So yes, she likes watching\Nyou suffer tremendously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,It's that simple?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.73,Main,,0,0,0,,She's made it clear\Nhow petty she can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:45.69,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll just keep pushing back.\NFind new ways to torment you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.77,0:17:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Then that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.69,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna make her pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NWe'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO\N'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NOh. One last thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NAh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I know today wasn't\Nexactly great,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,but on the upside, you saw Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You two are the perfect team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be\Ntogether again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:12.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Mm-hmm! I feel like\Nwe're making progress already,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:15.05,Main,,0,0,0,,so it's only a matter of time.\NJust hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hitoe. Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSee ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NDisgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,They make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA'S MOM]\NAkira, Iona's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NHow has she been?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Better, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA'S MOM]\NOh, yes, all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:54.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You're welcome here any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad she has\Nsuch a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA'S MOM]\NAkira? Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm sorry. Go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.31,0:19:06.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:23.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm going to have\Nto ask for another favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NAkira...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:34.01,Main,,0,0,0,,So precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:51.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI can't stomach that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NAnd her stupid smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHuh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You really think\NFumio Futase lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, unless she was\Nlying to us in the e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous, my heart's\Ngonna shoot into orbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Sorry, I know\Nit's hard to believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.02,Main,,0,0,0,,but she can be pretty\Nshy sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] Oh my gosh, oh my\Ngosh, oh my gosh, oh my gosh,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,oh my gosh, oh my gosh, oh my\Ngosh, oh my gooooshhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI whines, squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[doorbell]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:44.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, um. This is Ruko--you\Nsent me an e-mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NUh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, may we come in, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:18.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NAnyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:23.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NSo what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NWhite room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Large window.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,White room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Large window.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,White room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry we kind of just\Nlet ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[ALL gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Fumio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Fumio Futase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You know something about\NWIXOSS that we don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:36.71,Main,,0,0,0,,and I'd like to\Nhear what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO]\NBattle me for your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:40.84,Main,,0,0,0,,If you win, I'll tell you\Neverything you wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] How much do you\Nthink this author really knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[FUMIO] I've never seen\Nanything like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.84,0:23:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time: "This\NImpatience Isn't Awakening."
